                <text>phyllaries 40 – 60 in 5 – 6 series , sparsely puberulent to tomentulose , glabrescent , margins ciliolate , the outer lance_deltate to subulate , 1 – 3 mm , inner oblong , 4 – 7 + mm , tips acuminate to subulate or filiform .</text>
